<h1>Required Actions:Give Life to Our Vision</h4>
<br>
<br>
<h4>Introduction</h4>
<br>
<p>With a clear mental picture we can not must give our goals some life with a set of action steps or required_actions.
For instance, you want to start a new career. The require actions maybe developing the relevant skills, 
networking with people, and finding a job. Perhaps, you want to own a home. Now, you can think about how 
to get the house. It could be improving your credit, saving money, and hiring a real estate agent. Now, 
you want action steps for your goals.</p>

<h4>Pick a Vision</h4>
<form action="/requireds" method="Post">
<% @animates.each do |animate| %>
  <br><label><%= animate.name %></label>
   <input type="checkbox" name="animate[animate_ids][]" value="<%= animate.name %>"><br>
 <% end %>
<br>

<h4><label>What is an action step for your goal?</h4>
<br>
<textarea name="name" rows="1" cols="100"></textArea>
<br>
<br>
<h4><label>Describe what the action will require</label></h4>
<br>
<textarea name="description" rows="3" cols="100"></textArea>
<br>
<br>
<h4><label>Set a deadline for when you want to complete the step</label></h4>
<br>
<textarea name="deadline" rows="1" cols="100"></textArea>
<br>
<br>
<input type="submit" value="Create Action Step">
</form>



